Package: arjun
Version: 2.2.7
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: python, python-pip
Section: web
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/s0md3v/Arjun
Description: HTTP parameter discovery suite
 Arjun is a tool for finding HTTP parameters from web applications.
 It supports GET/POST methods, threading, and various filtering options.
